Package Project

Class Project

java.lang.Object
Project.Project
public class Project extends Object
Represents a project in a real estate system, which includes details about flats, officer assignments, and various filters such as availability, visibility, and date ranges.

      managerId - The ID of the project manager.
      officerSlots - The number of officer slots available for the project.
      assignedOfficers - A list of assigned officers for the project.
      visibility - The visibility status of the project (whether it's public or private).
      pendingOfficers - A list of officers who are pending assignment.
